<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-37"><a href="#.E5.B1.B1.E5.AF.A8.E5.B8.81"><span class="tocnumber">8</span> <span class="toctext">山寨币</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-38"><a href="#.E5.BB.B6.E4.BC.B8.E9.98.85.E8.AF.BB"><span class="tocnumber">9</span> <span class="toctext">延伸阅读</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-39"><a href="#.E5.8F.83.E8.80.83.E6.96.87.E7.8D.BB"><span class="tocnumber">10</span> <span class="toctext">參考文獻</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-40"><a href="#.E5.A4.96.E9.83.A8.E9.93.BE.E6.8E.A5"><span class="tocnumber">11</span> <span class="toctext">外部链接</span></a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<p></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id=".E4.BA.A4.E6.98.93">交易</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B8%81&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="编辑段落：交易">编辑</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="rellink boilerplate further noprint">更多資料：<a href="/w/index.php?title=%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B9%A3%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="比特幣協議（页面不存在）">比特幣協議</a></div>
<p>和电子邮件一样，比特币使用费用几乎是零。一次性大额交易量，为了加快交易速度，比特币对等网络节点（比特币矿工）会收取少量费用。在2014年3月，每笔交易的手续费一般是0.0001btc。</p>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id=".E8.BB.9F.E9.AB.94"><span id="Client"></span>軟體</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=%E6%AF%94%E7%89%B9%E5%B8%81&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="编辑段落：軟體">编辑</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Electrum_Bitcoin_Wallet.png" class="image"><img alt="" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/16/Electrum_Bitcoin_Wallet.png/220px-Electrum_Bitcoin_Wallet.png" width="220" height="123" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/16/Electrum_Bitcoin_Wallet.png/330px-Electrum_Bitcoin_Wallet.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/16/Electrum_Bitcoin_Wallet.png 2x" data-file-width="405" data-file-height="226" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Electrum_Bitcoin_Wallet.png" class="internal" title="放大"><img src="//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.24wmf12/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
「Electrum」是許多比特幣客戶端軟體的其中之一</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>比特币是类似<a href="/wiki/%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6" title="电子邮件">电子邮件</a>的电子现金，和收发<a href="/wiki/%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E9%82%AE%E4%BB%B6" title="电子邮件">电子邮件</a>相似，汇款方通过电脑或智能手机，按收款方地址将比特币直接付给对方。下列表格，列出了免费下载比特币钱包软件的部分网站。</p>
